## This repository accompanies the manuscripts: 
## Byungwook Choi, Peter Tiffin
## Department of Plant and Microbial Biology, University of Minnesota

## For ALL Raw datasets 
## Dataset List included:
- WGCNA_readcounts.csv: Raw read counts from dual-seq transcriptome profiles in this study (filtered by mean number of mapped reads > 10, referred to Table S2)
- Data_TPM.zip: Gene-level expression profiles (TPM) across entire libraries (compressed, *.csv)
- Data_TPM_cdlg.zip: Gene-level expression profiles (TPM/codinglength) across entirhe libraries (compressed, *.csv)
- Data_Log2TPM.zip: Gene-level expression profiles (Log2(TPM+1)) across entirhe libraries (compressed, *.csv)
